title: Shieldwall
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Models with this special rule treat friendly [[Hive Tyrant]]s (including the [[Swarmlord]]) exactly as though they were [[Independent Character]]s. 

A [[Hive Tyrant]] (or the [[Swarmlord]]) in a unit that contains at least one model with this special rule automatically passes Look Out, Sir! rolls.